Database Contents — Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0 (applies to DATA)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The contents of the `data/` directory constitute a database made available
under the Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0.

The canonical, full text of the ODbL v1.0 is published at:

    https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1-0/

By using the database contents you agree to the terms of that license. In
brief, and without overriding the canonical text above, the ODbL v1.0 permits
you to share, create from, and adapt the database provided that you attribute
The Sakshi Project, keep the database (or any adapted database) open under the
same terms, and, if you publicly use an adapted version, offer that adapted
database under the ODbL as well.

The data records a civic-accountability index of PUBLICLY REPORTED cases. It
is not a crime-rate statistic, not legal advice, and not a substitute for
official NCRB data. Every record carries its own public sources.
